    <item>
      <title>以色列对真主党采取的新危险态势并未引发战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/inside-israel-s-risky-new-posture-against-hezbollah</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列对黎巴嫩真主党采取了更危险、更激进的姿态 — — 爆炸传呼机、袭击贝鲁特并瞄准指挥官 — — 这一转变既是突然的，也是渐进的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/inside-israel-s-risky-new-posture-against-hezbollah</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 14:02:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>传呼机袭击致中东局势陷入危机，加沙协议希望破灭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/gaza-deal-hopes-sputter-as-pager-attacks-bring-mideast-to-brink</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国务卿安东尼·布林肯本周飞往中东，自去年 10 月 7 日以来他第 10 次访问中东，但他并不抱太大希望，认为这将有助于加沙战争取得突破。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/gaza-deal-hopes-sputter-as-pager-attacks-bring-mideast-to-brink</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗国家电视台称，伊朗在波斯湾举行最大规模海军演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/iran-holds-its-largest-naval-drills-in-persian-gulf-state-tv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据伊朗国家电视台报道，伊朗军队与伊斯兰革命卫队在该国南部海域举行了迄今为止最大规模的联合海军演习。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/iran-holds-its-largest-naval-drills-in-persian-gulf-state-tv</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 12:26:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞秋·里夫斯有六周时间通过新经济计划提振英国人情绪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/rachel-reeves-has-six-weeks-to-lift-uk-mood-with-new-economic-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷切尔·里夫斯有六周的时间来制定计划，以修复英国不完善的公共服务、促进经济发展并消除低迷的国民情绪 — — 并且不会破坏国家的财政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/rachel-reeves-has-six-weeks-to-lift-uk-mood-with-new-economic-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>无人机引爆武器库 俄罗斯疏散 1200 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/russia-evacuates-1-200-after-drone-ignites-weapons-site-blaze</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当地官员称，一架被击落的乌克兰无人机的残骸导致俄罗斯南部克拉斯诺达尔地区的一座弹药库发生大火，约 1,200 人被疏散。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/russia-evacuates-1-200-after-drone-ignites-weapons-site-blaze</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 10:24:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本地震灾区洪水致一人死亡，多人失踪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/floods-leave-one-dead-many-missing-in-quake-hit-area-of-japan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本北部沿海地区今年年初发生强烈地震，暴雨导致洪水泛滥，至少造成一人死亡，数人失踪，该地区目前仍在恢复中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/floods-leave-one-dead-many-missing-in-quake-hit-area-of-japan</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 08:57:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>二十国集团同意推动全球治理机构改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/g-20-agrees-to-push-for-reform-of-global-governance-institutions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过一个半月的谈判，二十国集团取得突破，同意推动联合国、世界贸易组织和多边贷款机构的改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/g-20-agrees-to-push-for-reform-of-global-governance-institutions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 06:08:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡选举竞争激烈，IMF资金面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/sri-lankans-vote-in-tight-race-that-puts-imf-funding-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两年前，斯里兰卡的经济崩溃和历史性的债务违约引发了广泛的政治动荡，并导致前强人领导人下台，此次至关重要的总统选举最终结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/sri-lankans-vote-in-tight-race-that-puts-imf-funding-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基敦促拜登邀请其加入北约并保证提供武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/zelenskiy-to-push-us-for-nato-invite-weapons-guarantees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泽连斯基将敦促美国总统拜登正式邀请乌克兰加入北约，并承诺持续供应先进武器，作为乌克兰总统结束与俄罗斯战争的“胜利计划”的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/zelenskiy-to-push-us-for-nato-invite-weapons-guarantees</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 20:22:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列加大对真主党的攻击力度，杀死最高指挥官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/israel-carries-out-precision-strike-in-hezbollah-stronghold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[星期五，以色列在贝鲁特南部郊区的空袭中杀死了真主党的一名高级指挥官。几天前的一系列袭击引发了人们对两方冲突可能失控的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/israel-carries-out-precision-strike-in-hezbollah-stronghold</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 13:47:06 GMT</pubDate>
